<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Turtle Shelter Project</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            color: #333;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #869986;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 1.5em;
        }

        nav {
            position: relative;
        }

        nav a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #fff;
            margin: 0 15px;
            font-size: 1em;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }

        .dropdown {
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .dropdown .dropbtn {
            background: none;
            border: none;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 1em;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-family: inherit;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .dropdown-content {
            display: none;
            position: absolute;
            background-color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0px 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            min-width: 150px;
            z-index: 1;
            border-radius: 5px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .dropdown-content a {
            color: #333;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: block;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
        }

        .dropdown-content a:hover {
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }

        .dropdown:hover .dropdown-content {
            display: block;
        }

        .content {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .content h1 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
        }

        .content p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #666;
            text-align: justify;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .content ul {
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding-left: 40px;
        }

        .content ul li {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .banner {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .button-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .button-container a {
            text-decoration: none;
            background-color: #869986;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 1em;
            border-radius: 5px;
            display: inline-block;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .button-container a:hover {
            background-color: #6f7c6f;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 0;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Turtle Shelter Project</h1>
        <nav>
            <a href="/">Home</a>
            <div class="dropdown">
                <button class="dropbtn">How You Can Help</button>
                <div class="dropdown-content">
                    <a href="/donate">Donate</a>
                    <a href="/event">Schedule an Event</a>
                    <a href="/volunteer">Volunteer From Home</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <div class="content">
        <img src="/Users/cocoli/Turtle-Shell-INTEX/img/volunteerbanner.jpg" alt="Volunteer from Home" class="banner">
        <h1>Volunteer From Home</h1>
        <p>
            You can do some of the sewing or other steps of the production process at home! Indicate in the form below what you would like to do. Please include your sewing skill level:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>No sewing:</strong> Can cut, pin, and mark vest components.</li>
            <li><strong>Beginning sewing:</strong> Just learning to use a sewing machine.</li>
            <li><strong>Basic sewing:</strong> Can sew a straight stitch.</li>
            <li><strong>Advanced sewing:</strong> Can handle challenging sewing tasks.</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="button-container">
            <a href="/volunteer">Go to Volunteer Form</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        &copy; 2024 Turtle Shelter Project
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
